```pseudocode
//Kim ya fara sana'ar kula da gida kuma yana lissafin yawan ribar da zai samu daga abokan cinikinsa.
//Yana da abokan ciniki 3 a yanzu, amma yana magana da wasu 5 masu yuwuwar kasancewa abokan ciniki kuma yana jin ƙarfin gwuiwar samun su ya haɗa dasu cikin lissafinsa.
//Gidan kowane abokin ciniki zai buƙaci kwalabe 2 na sinadarin wanki da yankin tsumma don tsaftacewa gida guda.
//kwalabe na sinadarin wankin zai kai $2 kowanne, shi kuma yankin tsumma zai kai $5 kowanne.
//Waɗannan su ne kawai kuɗin da zai kashe.
//Ya ƙididdige cewa jimillar kuɗin shigar kowane mako zai zama $92.
//Riba ita ce bambanci tsakanin jimillar kuɗin shiga da kuma kuɗi, don haka ribar nawa, a lissafin dala, Lucas zai samu kowane mako?

//Hafta na abokan ciniki da ke da shi a farkin labarin
num abokan_ciniki_a_farko = 3

//Hafta na abokan ciniki da zai iya zama
num abokan_ciniki_da_yuwuwar = 5

//Kayan kwari na sinadarin wanki kowane gida
num kuɗi_sinadarin_wanki = 2

//Kayan kwari na yankin tsumma kowane gida
num kuɗi_yankin_tsumma = 5

//Jimillar kuɗin shigar gida guda
num jimillar_kuɗi = abokan_ciniki_a_farko * (kuɗi_sinadarin_wanki + kuɗi_yankin_tsumma)

//Jimillar kuɗin shiga
num jimillar_kuɗi_shiga = abokan_ciniki_a_farko + abokan_ciniki_da_yuwuwar * (kuɗi_sinadarin_wanki + kuɗi_yankin_tsumma)

//Riba
num riba = jimillar_kuɗi_shiga - jimillar_kuɗi

//Riba a lissafin dala
print(riba)
```
Amsar ita ce 92.
